		</li>
		<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 78px">
			<div class="thumb" style="width: 76px;"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Gravure_La_Commune_de_Paris.jpg" class="mw-file-description" title="A poster from the Paris Commune (1871)"><img alt="A poster from the Paris Commune (1871)" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/48/Gravure_La_Commune_de_Paris.jpg/114px-Gravure_La_Commune_de_Paris.jpg" decoding="async" width="76" height="100" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/48/Gravure_La_Commune_de_Paris.jpg/170px-Gravure_La_Commune_de_Paris.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/48/Gravure_La_Commune_de_Paris.jpg/227px-Gravure_La_Commune_de_Paris.jpg 2x" data-file-width="1659" data-file-height="2190" /></a></span></div>
